Project description

netCDF version 4 has many features not found in earlier versions of the library,such as hierarchical groups, zlib compression, multiple unlimited dimensions,and new data types. It is implemented on top of HDF5. This module implementsmost of the new features, and can read and write netCDF files compatible witholder versions of the library. The API is modelled after Scientific.IO.NetCDF,and should be familiar to users of that module.
